happy hour's starting early.

13:54.784 --> 13:55.917
<font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS)</font>

13:55.952 --> 13:58.152
Wait for me, ya dickheads!

13:58.187 --> 14:00.988
<font color="#ffff00">(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS, LAUGHTER)</font>

14:01.024 --> 14:05.092
♪

14:05.128 --> 14:09.697
And I already have
a prototype for the claw.

14:09.732 --> 14:12.199
Bet you a hundo I can pick up
a single peanut.

14:14.671 --> 14:16.904
Damn it! It was working good before.

14:16.940 --> 14:18.272
Yeah, it's a great idea for a restaurant.

14:18.308 --> 14:21.809
But you know what else was
a really great idea?

14:21.844 --> 14:23.644
Earth.
Nah.

14:23.680 --> 14:25.546
Come on, you said it yourself...
It's a mess.

14:25.581 --> 14:27.315
I mean, look at all those prayers.

14:27.350 --> 14:28.768
They're impossible.

14:29.652 --> 14:30.918
Maybe I can... I can help.

14:30.954 --> 14:33.988
You couldn't answer
a single one of those.

14:36.317 --> 14:39.093
You wanna make a bet?

14:39.737 --> 14:41.295
A bet?

14:41.331 --> 14:42.563
You hear that, Sanjay?

14:42.598 --> 14:44.432
A bet. <font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS)</font>

14:44.467 --> 14:46.100
Interesting.

14:46.135 --> 14:47.535
You thinking a hundo?
Mm...

14:47.570 --> 14:50.271
I was thinking something
a little higher-stakes.

14:50.306 --> 14:52.006
Ohh! A thouso?

14:54.143 --> 14:55.843
Bigger.

14:55.878 --> 14:59.380
If I answer one of these
"Impossible" prayers,

14:59.415 --> 15:01.048
you spare Earth.

15:01.084 --> 15:04.685
A-All right. All right.

15:04.721 --> 15:07.188
But. If you fail...

15:07.223 --> 15:08.322
The Earth explodes.

15:08.358 --> 15:10.558
Yeah, but, also...

15:10.593 --> 15:14.428
you have to eat a worm.

15:14.464 --> 15:16.263
Alive. The whole thing.

15:16.299 --> 15:18.666
The head and the butt.
In front of everyone.

15:18.701 --> 15:19.867
And you have to act like you like it.

15:19.902 --> 15:21.902
You have to go, "Mmm. Oh-ho!

15:21.938 --> 15:24.171
Mmm. Yum. I like worms."

15:24.207 --> 15:25.906
<font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS)</font> Hey!

15:25.942 --> 15:27.475
Did you hear that, Sanjay?
Isn't that great?

15:27.510 --> 15:29.120
Very funny.

15:30.113 --> 15:31.779
All right. Good luck.

15:31.814 --> 15:34.982
♪

15:35.018 --> 15:36.517
How long do I have?

15:37.059 --> 15:38.819
Two weeks.
How about a month?

15:38.855 --> 15:41.022
Two weeks!

15:41.057 --> 15:42.757
Oh.

15:43.885 --> 15:46.293
<font color="#ff0000">WOMAN:</font> Prayer 98% complete.

15:46.329 --> 15:48.763
Great news! I figured it out.

15:48.798 --> 15:50.865
Please not now.
Listen, I made a bet with God,

15:50.900 --> 15:52.700
and all we have to do to save the world

15:52.735 --> 15:53.901
is answer one of these...

15:53.936 --> 15:55.369
Please just leave me alone.

15:55.405 --> 15:56.670
Craig, this is a big deal!

15:56.706 --> 15:58.005
Come on!
Oh!

15:58.041 --> 16:00.541
Oh!
Minor earthquake.

16:00.576 --> 16:01.809
That was hours of work.

16:01.844 --> 16:03.878
So what? It's just a missing glove.

16:03.913 --> 16:05.546
Who cares about gloves?
I do!

16:05.581 --> 16:06.881
I care about gloves!

16:06.916 --> 16:09.450
I care about gloves!

16:09.485 --> 16:10.718
No, look, I know.

16:10.753 --> 16:13.020
You think what I do is small

16:13.056 --> 16:15.589
and stupid and insignificant.

16:15.625 --> 16:17.291
But it is my life.

16:17.710 --> 16:20.027
I-I don't have anything else.

16:20.063 --> 16:21.429
All right, the rest of you are fine.

16:21.464 --> 16:24.198
You just go around.
"Oh, let's go grab a burger.

16:24.233 --> 16:26.300
Let's all socialize,
get burgers together.

16:26.335 --> 16:28.769
Let's go to a party and have...

16:28.805 --> 16:30.237
burgers," or however it goes...

16:30.273 --> 16:33.441
I don't know how it goes.
Maybe I will never know.

16:33.851 --> 16:36.177
But I knew about my job.

16:36.212 --> 16:38.846
I was good at that, at least.

16:38.881 --> 16:40.815
And you've taken that away from me.

16:40.850 --> 16:43.067
♪

16:43.119 --> 16:44.819
<font color="#ffff00">(DOOR OPENS, CLOSES)</font>

16:46.916 --> 16:51.378
♪

16:51.379 --> 16:54.499
_

16:54.524 --> 17:01.896
♪

17:01.931 --> 17:07.769
♪

17:09.209 --> 17:10.708
<font color="#ffff00">(COMPUTER POWERS ON)</font>

17:10.743 --> 17:13.077
Please. I really need my glove.

17:13.113 --> 17:18.249
♪

17:18.285 --> 17:22.119
♪

17:22.155 --> 17:23.221
<font color="#ffff00">(BAG THUDS)</font>

17:23.256 --> 17:25.805
Oh, good. You're here.

17:25.839 --> 17:26.991
