17:27.027 --> 17:28.560
Oh, I just, uh...

17:28.596 --> 17:31.429
I wanted to make sure
you got the last leaf.

17:37.337 --> 17:39.237
Ah! My glove!

17:39.272 --> 17:41.639
<font color="#ff0000">WOMAN:</font> Prayer complete.

17:42.742 --> 17:45.076
Well, no, you should stamp it.

17:45.111 --> 17:47.212
You sure?
Absolutely.

17:47.247 --> 17:48.847
It was a team effort.

17:53.019 --> 17:54.252
<font color="#ffff00">(GUNSHOT)</font>

17:54.974 --> 17:57.922
Time to kill. <font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS MANIACALLY)</font>

17:57.958 --> 17:59.390
F7?
Yeah, F7.

17:59.426 --> 18:00.725
<font color="#ff0000">Whoo! Woman:</font> Mute.

18:00.760 --> 18:03.328
<font color="#ffff00">(SIGHS)</font>

18:07.934 --> 18:09.868
That's a lot to go through.

18:10.281 --> 18:11.936
We should probably get started.

18:11.972 --> 18:15.707
♪

18:15.742 --> 18:17.942
Maybe we can do it over burgers?

18:17.978 --> 18:19.644
Burgers?

18:20.208 --> 18:21.913
"Please save the rainforest."

18:21.948 --> 18:24.849
Impossible. "Please stop all wars." No.

18:24.885 --> 18:27.352
"Please make everyone
just chill out on Twitter."

18:27.387 --> 18:29.220
"Wi-Fi."
"Wi-Fi."

18:29.256 --> 18:30.889
"Airport Wi-Fi."
"Wi-Fi."

18:30.924 --> 18:32.690
"Wi-Fi."

18:33.526 --> 18:36.794
<font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS)</font> Craig, come on!

18:39.266 --> 18:40.999
Craig, leave 'em!

18:41.034 --> 18:44.202
Uh, it was really nice meeting you.

18:44.237 --> 18:45.858
You too.

18:47.841 --> 18:49.874
<font color="#ffff00">(BOTH CHUCKLE)</font>

18:49.910 --> 18:51.276
♪

18:51.311 --> 18:52.677
<font color="#ffff00">(SIGHS)</font>

18:52.712 --> 18:56.180
Please, if anybody is listening...

18:56.216 --> 18:57.849
I really like this girl.

18:57.884 --> 18:59.751
Just please make this happen.

18:59.786 --> 19:01.920
No. No, no, no, no, no.

19:01.955 --> 19:03.922
Okay, love prayers never work, all right?

19:03.957 --> 19:05.657
There's... There's too many variables.

19:05.692 --> 19:07.892
So, that girl he likes
could be uninterested in him,

19:07.928 --> 19:09.861
or she could be in love
with somebody else.

19:09.896 --> 19:12.330
But check it out.

19:12.365 --> 19:14.365
Related prayer.

19:17.370 --> 19:18.536
<font color="#ffff00">(VIDEO REWINDING)</font>

19:18.571 --> 19:20.505
<font color="#ffff00">(KEYBOARD CLACKS, BEEP)</font>

19:20.540 --> 19:23.841
♪

19:23.877 --> 19:26.577
Please, if you're listening...

19:26.613 --> 19:29.569
I really like this guy.

19:30.450 --> 19:31.616
Please make this happen.

19:31.651 --> 19:32.951
<font color="#ffff00">(KEYBOARD CLACKS)</font>

19:32.986 --> 19:34.652
♪

19:35.322 --> 19:37.455
This could work.

19:46.908 --> 19:49.442
I don't know.
These prayers seem kinda vague.

19:49.478 --> 19:51.511
