20:01.134 --> 20:02.567
Yeah, I don't know.

20:02.602 --> 20:05.484
I think they really have to,
like, you know, "do it."

20:05.519 --> 20:07.019
Right?
Two dates.

20:07.019 --> 20:08.118
And they hold hands.

20:08.154 --> 20:09.386
I think it needs to be full sex.

20:09.422 --> 20:11.789
How about a kiss?
Ooh, a kiss!

20:12.320 --> 20:15.059
Romantic. Ha. Little Casanova over here.

20:15.094 --> 20:16.894
<font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS)</font> I like it.

20:16.929 --> 20:18.595
Rosie? Bring it in.

20:18.631 --> 20:27.371
♪

20:27.406 --> 20:29.594
<font color="#ff0000">WOMAN:</font> Earth destruction in two weeks.

20:29.629 --> 20:30.934
All right, wait a minute.

20:30.969 --> 20:33.711
Eliza, are you sure you want this prayer?

20:33.746 --> 20:37.147
