that world-explody thing,

20:37.183 --> 20:39.550
there's no turning back.
<font color="#ffff00">(BOMB TICKING)</font>

20:39.585 --> 20:43.610
I don't want you crying when
everybody starts calling you

20:43.635 --> 20:45.802
"Worm Breath."

20:46.012 --> 20:47.979
What?
I'm sure.

20:48.127 --> 20:49.960
All right. It's a bet.

20:49.995 --> 20:51.228
<font color="#ffff00">(POPS LIPS)</font>

20:51.263 --> 20:52.763
Bet is made.

20:52.798 --> 20:55.071
<font color="#ffff00">(LAUGHS)</font>

20:56.302 --> 21:00.112
You just picked
the hardest prayer in the box!

21:00.137 --> 21:01.303
Uh... n...

21:01.328 --> 21:03.328
It doesn't seem that hard.

21:03.353 --> 21:06.054
I mean, these two people,
they really like each other.

21:06.245 --> 21:08.011
They... They get along, they're...

21:08.047 --> 21:10.447
they have fun together, they're
in close physical proximity.

21:10.483 --> 21:12.182
