21:12.218 --> 21:13.450
Right, Craig?

21:13.486 --> 21:14.852
Right. Yes. <font color="#ffff00">(CLEARS THROAT)</font>

21:14.887 --> 21:16.420
Uh, should be simple.

21:16.455 --> 21:18.478
Hey, you shaved.
Did I?

21:18.514 --> 21:19.970
Yes, I did.

21:20.526 --> 21:22.726
You ready?
Let's do it.

21:25.431 --> 21:27.331
No, sir, love ain't easy.

21:27.366 --> 21:29.266
<font color="#ffff00">(DOOR CLOSES)</font>

21:29.301 --> 21:31.268
She is gonna eat that worm.

21:31.303 --> 21:34.104
<font color="#ffff00">(WOMAN VOCALIZING)</font>

